is is because, insofar as physical forms are \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":130,\"end\":287}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"limitless\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":287,\"end\":296},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"ea37366c-4caa-4d9f-b7db-bde18445f43b\",\"uuid\":\"23e75437-cd66-4393-b2a4-efc3308ebec6\",\"toh\":\"toh12\"}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\", a bodhisattva should be known as \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":296,\"end\":331}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"limitless\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":331,\"end\":340},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"ea37366c-4caa-4d9f-b7db-bde18445f43b\",\"uuid\":\"f855891f-7684-44cf-b159-0bb0d38b1855\",\"toh\":\"toh12\"}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\".\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":340,\"end\":341},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"endNoteLink\",\"attrs\":{\"notes\":[{\"endNote\":\"db04e5d3-67bf-4362-81ce-bb9347f23317\",\"label\":\"178\",\"uuid\":\"6fdbe209-d3a0-4148-9b25-1f9efca8a0af\",\"start\":341,\"end\":341,\"location\":\"end\",\"toh\":null}]}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\" Likewise, insofar as feelings, conceptions, conditioning factors, and consciousness are \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":341,\"end\":430}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"limitless\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":430,\"end\":439},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"ea37366c-4caa-4d9f-b7db-bde18445f43b\",\"uuid\":\"544671cd-57a8-4985-9e3e-79cced68f73e\",\"toh\":\"toh12\"}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\", a bodhisattva should be known as \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":439,\"end\":474}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"limitless\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":474,\"end\":483},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"ea37366c-4caa-4d9f-b7db-bde18445f43b\",\"uuid\":\"a28eea9d-fd35-4eaf-b565-41185e185bae\",\"toh\":\"toh12\"}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\". He or she does not go close to the thought, ‘Bodhisattvas are physical forms.’ Even this thought is not found and not mentally perceived. Likewise, he or she does not go close to the thought, ‘Bodhisattvas are feelings, conceptions, conditioning factors, and consciousness.’ Even this thought is not found and not mentally perceived. O \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":483,\"end\":821}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Blessed One\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":821,\"end\":832},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"7bf45dd5-3e8d-4495-bc65-ecf0a51d3597\",\"uuid\":\"d6d14c44-b820-49f8-ad79-96083bb58b26\",\"toh\":\"toh12\"}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\", since I am \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":832,\"end\":845}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"not mentally perceiving\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":845,\"end\":868},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"028c8c16-0513-4dae-9e1b-14c834880ede\",\"uuid\":\"126683b1-6c90-4de5-8f79-10b8c14c70bf\",\"toh\":\"toh12\"}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\" any such thing called a ‘bodhisattva’ anywhere at all or in any way at all, I do not identify this thing designated to be a ‘bodhisattva.’\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":868,\"end\":1007},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"endNoteLink\",\"attrs\":{\"notes\":[{\"endNote\":\"1dcab667-fb5b-4977-90e5-ca6ed7547dbd\",\"label\":\"179\",\"uuid\":\"0462d82c-6090-476b-8dc5-e3a14c33b33a\",\"start\":1007,\"end\":1007,\"location\":\"end\",\"toh\":null}]}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\" Nor do I identify or mentally perceive the perfection of wisdom. Nor do I identify or mentally perceive the \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":1007,\"end\":1116}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"state of complete knowing\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":1116,\"end\":1141},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"f1f21402-d1eb-4ca2-b32a-df9dbdf949a5\",\"uuid\":\"b441dd8c-a8a6-499f-a7b6-025859f6ff3c\",\"toh\":\"toh12\"}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\". O \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":1141,\"end\":1145}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Blessed One\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":1145,\"end\":1156},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"7bf45dd5-3e8d-4495-bc65-ecf0a51d3597\",\"uuid\":\"6c3d1e06-0a43-42da-8887-72e2fc478950\",\"toh\":\"toh12\"}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\", since I myself am neither mentally perceiving nor identifying that thing anywhere at all by any means at all, what thing should I instruct and guide in what thing by means of what thing? O \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":1156,\"end\":1347}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Blessed One\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":1347,\"end\":1358},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"7bf45dd5-3e8d-4495-bc65-ecf0a51d3597\",\"uuid\":\"15e16bbb-6fe5-4de3-91eb-7d5e1d37fbd1\",\"toh\":\"toh12\"}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\", this ‘buddha’ is a mere designation. O \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":1358,\"end\":1399}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Blessed One\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":1399,\"end\":1410},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"7bf45dd5-3e8d-4495-bc65-ecf0a51d3597\",\"uuid\":\"b802e9cb-d15c-4c58-8c95-5c2e628b6ea3\",\"toh\":\"toh12\"}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\", this ‘bodhisattva’ is a mere designation. O \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":1410,\"end\":1456}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Blessed One\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":1456,\"end\":1467},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"7bf45dd5-3e8d-4495-bc65-ecf0a51d3597\",\"uuid\":\"5764529f-e493-4c95-abff-4dc2213bc8e7\",\"toh\":\"toh12\"}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\", this ‘perfection of wisdom’ is a mere designation. But these designations have not truly come into being.\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":1467,\"end\":1574},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"endNoteLink\",\"attrs\":{\"notes\":[{\"endNote\":\"8f4d02c1-0fc9-495d-b78c-e4e73680ac02\",\"label\":\"180\",\"uuid\":\"3090bd92-e6a2-4837-a3ac-0a5ed9f970ee\",\"start\":1574,\"end\":1574,\"location\":\"end\",\"toh\":null}]}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\" O \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":1574,\"end\":1577}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Blessed One\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":1577,\"end\":1588},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"7bf45dd5-3e8d-4495-bc65-ecf0a51d3597\",\"uuid\":\"0589a467-aafc-4bae-95a8-ebea9583a225\",\"toh\":\"toh12\"}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\", it is just like the fact that the word \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":1588,\"end\":1629}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"self\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":1629,\"end\":1633},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"italic\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":1629,\"end\":1633,\"uuid\":\"e2a0ff79-649a-45ea-8566-4e5531565646\",\"type\":\"span\",\"textStyle\":\"distinct\"}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\" is said, but a self absolutely has not truly come into being.\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":1633,\"end\":1695},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"endNoteLink\",\"attrs\":{\"notes\":[{\"endNote\":\"9f1ed5c3-4ae4-4350-a480-a07f9641f27f\",\"label\":\"181\",\"uuid\":\"cd3b2ba1-6a4c-4a92-a5cf-e9a23d22eced\",\"start\":1695,\"end\":1695,\"location\":\"end\",\"toh\":null}]}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\" Similarly, all things have the \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":1695,\"end\":1727}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"inherent nature\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":1727,\"end\":1742},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"d0454d45-c368-446c-b993-0bd0e6679719\",\"uuid\":\"1af40640-3b46-4d88-a8eb-05c7017fef4c\",\"toh\":\"toh12\"}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\" of lacking any state of being.\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":1742,\"end\":1773},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"endNoteLink\",\"attrs\":{\"notes\":[{\"endNote\":\"92855f27-f582-4228-9764-a59c644629d8\",\"label\":\"182\",\"uuid\":\"5e358e6d-aa92-4b3a-94cf-48c4c80f505b\",\"start\":1773,\"end\":1773,\"location\":\"end\",\"toh\":null}]}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\" What are those physical forms that have not truly come into being and cannot be grasped? What are those feelings, conceptions, conditioning factors, and consciousness that have not truly come into being and cannot be grasped? The condition for all these things to be \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":1773,\"end\":2041}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"free of inherent nature\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":2041,\"end\":2064},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"3689e652-c404-47d7-a8b6-de95e649587b\",\"uuid\":\"015df638-834e-4a72-90e1-b3841f0e7374\",\"toh\":\"toh12\"}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\" in this way is their \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":2064,\"end\":2086}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"not truly coming into being\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":2086,\"end\":2113},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"169b497b-90ea-4a3b-83ea-4c9a94a20c99\",\"uuid\":\"bdef0016-3904-42ef-aa57-a82bfdb196b7\",\"toh\":\"toh12\"}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\", and yet those things’ \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":2113,\"end\":2137}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"not truly coming into being\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":2137,\"end\":2164},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"169b497b-90ea-4a3b-83ea-4c9a94a20c99\",\"uuid\":\"0328c00b-79f6-4ff6-975e-b7fda8ba29f9\",\"toh\":\"toh12\"}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\" is not those things themselves. How then shall I instruct and guide someone who is \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":2164,\"end\":2248}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"not truly coming into being\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":2248,\"end\":2275},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"169b497b-90ea-4a3b-83ea-4c9a94a20c99\",\"uuid\":\"36225d92-c979-4fbe-9c4f-20aedb91d6b4\",\"toh\":\"toh12\"}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\" in the perfection of wisdom that also is \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":2275,\"end\":2317}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"not truly coming into being\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":2317,\"end\":2344},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"169b497b-90ea-4a3b-83ea-4c9a94a20c99\",\"uuid\":\"9d2daf90-5ffb-476f-801b-dae1d9317ec1\",\"toh\":\"toh12\"}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"?\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":2344,\"end\":2345},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"endNoteLink\",\"attrs\":{\"notes\":[{\"endNote\":\"70c1be5e-8646-47d5-9f61-95e4c9d2fa2f\",\"label\":\"183\",\"uuid\":\"84bb7fe3-fd4b-40d6-9c77-7a74b4617779\",\"start\":2345,\"end\":2345,\"location\":\"end\",\"toh\":null}]}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\" O Bhagavan, no things‍—whether they be things constituting buddhas, constituting bodhisattvas, or constituting anyone who might practice to awaken‍—are mentally perceived anywhere other than in their \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":2345,\"end\":2546}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"not truly coming into being\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":2546,\"end\":2573},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"169b497b-90ea-4a3b-83ea-4c9a94a20c99\",\"uuid\":\"0a612004-f18d-4923-bd89-79c4f16ac9d9\",\"toh\":\"toh12\"}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\".\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":2573,\"end\":2574}}]}]},{\"type\":\"passage\",\"attrs\":{\"uuid\":\"29118948-f08f-41a6-9a44-55171ecb45c9\",\"sort\":12393,\"type\":\"translation\",\"label\":\"1.91\",\"alignments\":{\"toh12\":{\"folioUuid\":\"c222691f-5426-4fd0-8cd8-beb07b535a78\",\"toh\":\"toh12\",\"tibetan\":\"$5f\",\"folioNumber\":15,\"volumeNumber\":33}}},\"content\":[{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":0,\"end\":1652,\"uuid\":\"29118948-f08f-41a6-9a44-55171ecb45c9\"},\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"“O \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":0,\"end\":3}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Blessed One\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":3,\"end\":14},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"7bf45dd5-3e8d-4495-bc65-ecf0a51d3597\",\"uuid\":\"898e1a5b-3b50-4a42-be4c-f275559ebe95\",\"toh\":\"toh12\"}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\", when it is described in this way, taught in this way, and expounded in this way, if a bodhisattva \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":14,\"end\":114}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"great being\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":114,\"end\":125},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"be37efde-2f63-40d0-8e8e-e93b3b3a581e\",\"uuid\":\"a0f16dbe-8897-482f-915b-30bcb2899e41\",\"toh\":\"toh12\"}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"’s \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":125,\"end\":128}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"mindset\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":128,\"end\":135},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"ad0b5c96-5b65-496d-bb1c-0e4fa6ad3bf4\",\"uuid\":\"6bb221e0-6604-4540-9121-ac14abb20b04\",\"toh\":\"toh12\"}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\" does not become deflated, depressed, dejected, or \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":135,\"end\":186}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"sunk in despondency\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":186,\"end\":205},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"12850e8f-bca6-487d-b286-8a071e49491f\",\"uuid\":\"b614393b-8653-437c-a277-7d878712929f\",\"toh\":\"toh12\"}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\", and if his or her \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":205,\"end\":225}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"mental attitude\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":225,\"end\":240},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"71984920-52bd-485c-9f8f-1b4d1cb73d33\",\"uuid\":\"5b5f05c2-7568-49fc-8c9c-30c4977b37fc\",\"toh\":\"toh12\"}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\" does not become discouraged, shattered, frightened, terrified, or \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":240,\"end\":307}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"stricken with terror\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":307,\"end\":327},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"2683095c-4a8b-4b93-a0f5-cb42d263f8e2\",\"uuid\":\"0229c3b5-c5b9-4051-84af-115e07ccfdcb\",\"toh\":\"toh12\"}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\", then in this way it should be known that this bodhisattva \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":327,\"end\":387}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"great being\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":387,\"end\":398},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"be37efde-2f63-40d0-8e8e-e93b3b3a581e\",\"uuid\":\"8dae4bc1-4c64-403a-b474-d11a42819b68\",\"toh\":\"toh12\"}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\" \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":398,\"end\":399}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"goes about life\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":399,\"end\":414},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"e47cf8c1-4e22-4e6c-af2f-a5dac51c76a0\",\"uuid\":\"7639e2a1-f756-447b-a982-c7cfb23c2202\",\"toh\":\"toh12\"}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\" in the perfection of wisdom, this bodhisattva \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":414,\"end\":461}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"great being\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":461,\"end\":472},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"be37efde-2f63-40d0-8e8e-e93b3b3a581e\",\"uuid\":\"a3eb1868-01b5-44f9-9085-c86d6ea661e9\",\"toh\":\"toh12\"}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\" \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":472,\"end\":473}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"cultivates\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":473,\"end\":483},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"08ff4aa9-bae0-47bc-b36c-93ba28c249f0\",\"uuid\":\"74c47a3c-0c64-4ac7-8b2c-ec1e6562bac5\",\"toh\":\"toh12\"}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\" the perfection of wisdom, and this bodhisattva \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":483,\"end\":531}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"great being\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":531,\"end\":542},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"be37efde-2f63-40d0-8e8e-e93b3b3a581e\",\"uuid\":\"1567dedd-3e9a-4795-b774-afc2aec3b99d\",\"toh\":\"toh12\"}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\" reflects upon the perfection of wisdom. The bodhisattva \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":542,\"end\":599}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"great being\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":599,\"end\":610},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"be37efde-2f63-40d0-8e8e-e93b3b3a581e\",\"uuid\":\"9059b634-33d0-41ad-b468-720a26fac29d\",\"toh\":\"toh12\"}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\" meditates upon the perfection of wisdom. Why is that? It is because at the time when a bodhisattva investigates these things in the perfection of wisdom, he or she neither goes close to physical forms, nor arrives at them, nor identifies their arising, nor identifies their cessation. Likewise, he or she neither goes close to feelings, conceptions, conditioning factors, or consciousness, nor arrives at them, nor identifies their arising, nor identifies their cessation.\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":610,\"end\":1083},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"endNoteLink\",\"attrs\":{\"notes\":[{\"endNote\":\"2426b75d-f649-40e4-be04-ee96817ed526\",\"label\":\"184\",\"uuid\":\"3a788441-6edb-4570-a7cf-f7f0e7f5c2c2\",\"start\":1083,\"end\":1083,\"location\":\"end\",\"toh\":null}]}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\" Why is that? To explain, the characteristic of not arising that belongs to physical forms is not the same as the physical forms.\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":1083,\"end\":1212},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"endNoteLink\",\"attrs\":{\"notes\":[{\"endNote\":\"ae4c50bc-faf2-4b23-8e32-fa8c0fcba6ae\",\"label\":\"185\",\"uuid\":\"14252aef-c023-41da-a28e-76d73972f66e\",\"start\":1212,\"end\":1212,\"location\":\"end\",\"toh\":null}]}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\" The characteristic of not ceasing that belongs to physical forms is not the same as the physical forms.\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":1212,\"end\":1316},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"endNoteLink\",\"attrs\":{\"notes\":[{\"endNote\":\"ac21a312-f4b4-4754-b2dd-fd3b5dd7d8cf\",\"label\":\"186\",\"uuid\":\"97ac2401-112f-45e2-8666-0140e8bd3b30\",\"start\":1316,\"end\":1316,\"location\":\"end\",\"toh\":null}]}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\" This being said, the characteristic of not arising and the physical forms are something free of duality, and \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":1316,\"end\":1426}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"free from creating duality\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":1426,\"end\":1452},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"9fea1c3a-8171-4a64-b63b-3e1024aa180b\",\"uuid\":\"2258d067-b131-49c6-8377-0ec73fee53b6\",\"toh\":\"toh12\"}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\".\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":1452,\"end\":1453},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"endNoteLink\",\"attrs\":{\"notes\":[{\"endNote\":\"cc78e3e8-83ac-4898-8794-cb8f724a1e3e\",\"label\":\"187\",\"uuid\":\"bc2b37e2-289a-4712-b6d9-6fd213e8eb71\",\"start\":1453,\"end\":1453,\"location\":\"end\",\"toh\":null}]}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\" Also, the characteristic of not ceasing and the physical forms are something free of duality, and \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":1453,\"end\":1552}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"free from creating duality\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":1552,\"end\":1578},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"9fea1c3a-8171-4a64-b63b-3e1024aa180b\",\"uuid\":\"a572c084-45ce-4266-b028-dc4f66b30227\",\"toh\":\"toh12\"}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\".\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":1578,\"end\":1579},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"endNoteLink\",\"attrs\":{\"notes\":[{\"endNote\":\"02df0d16-01d1-4d86-86e5-ce2d119b855c\",\"label\":\"188\",\"uuid\":\"a1e1d07e-a3d0-4727-9fbf-2f86d7a0fb18\",\"start\":1579,\"end\":1579,\"location\":\"end\",\"toh\":null}]}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\" Again, saying ‘physical forms’ is to \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":1579,\"end\":1617}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"quantify\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":1617,\"end\":1625},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"da120fb0-fc39-419b-9f2e-d54611ad0639\",\"uuid\":\"6f3e90dd-dcb2-4dba-918b-707134569b5b\",\"toh\":\"toh12\"}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\" something free of duality.\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":1625,\"end\":1652},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"endNoteLink\",\"attrs\":{\"notes\":[{\"endNote\":\"36d818b3-0616-4b58-9e9b-2dffd6cf9891\",\"label\":\"189\",\"uuid\":\"5f30fcb2-b596-4b2b-a489-564c4333f600\",\"start\":1652,\"end\":1652,\"location\":\"end\",\"toh\":null}]}}]}]}]},{\"type\":\"passage\",\"attrs\":{\"uuid\":\"0c6a6f4c-1957-4ab9-9a62-056bc9469365\",\"sort\":12438,\"type\":\"translation\",\"label\":\"1.92\",\"alignments\":{\"toh12\":{\"folioUuid\":\"e3e90550-ca9b-49de-a681-4e1aa763fbcf\",\"toh\":\"toh12\",\"tibetan\":\"དེ་བཞིན་དུ་འདི་ལྟར་ཚོར་བའི་གང་ལགས་པ་དང་། འདུ་ཤེས་ཀྱི་གང་\\nལགས་པ་དང་འདུ་བྱེད་རྣམས་ཀྱི་གང་ལགས་པ་དང་། འདི་ལྟར་རྣམ་པར་ཤེས་པའི་སྐྱེ་བ་མ་མཆིས་པ་གང་ལགས་པ་དེ་ནི་རྣམ་པར་ཤེས་པ་མ་ལགས། རྣམ་པར་ཤེས་པའི་འཇིག་པ་མ་མཆིས་པ་གང་ལགས་པ་དེ་ནི་རྣམ་པར་ཤེས་པ་མ་ལགས་ཏེ། དེས་ན་སྐྱེ་བ་མ་\\nམཆིས་པ་དང་རྣམ་པར་ཤེས་པ་ཞེས་བགྱི་བ་འདི་ཡང་གཉིས་སུ་མ་མཆིས་ཤིང་གཉིས་སུ་བགྱིར་མ་མཆིས་སོ། །དེས་ན་འཇིག་པ་མ་མཆིས་པ་དང་རྣམ་པར་ཤེས་པ་ཞེས་བགྱི་བ་འདི་ཡང་གཉིས་སུ་མ་མཆིས་ཤིང་གཉིས་སུ་བགྱིར་མ་མཆིས་ཏེ། གང་ཡང་འདི་སྐད་དུ་རྣམ་པར་\\nཤེས་པ་ཞེས་བགྱི་བ་འདི་ནི་གཉིས་སུ་མ་མཆིས་པའི་གྲངས་སུ་གཏོགས་སོ། །\",\"folioNumber\":15,\"volumeNumber\":33}}},\"content\":[{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":0,\"end\":861,\"uuid\":\"0c6a6f4c-1957-4ab9-9a62-056bc9469365\"},\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"“Likewise, the characteristic of not arising that belongs to feelings, conceptions, conditioning factors, and consciousness is not the same as the so-called feelings, conceptions, conditioning factors, and consciousness. The characteristic of not ceasing that belongs to feelings, conceptions, conditioning factors, and consciousness is not the same as the so-called consciousness. This being said, the characteristic of not arising and the feelings, conceptions, conditioning factors, and consciousness are something free of duality, and \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":0,\"end\":539}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"free from creating duality\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":539,\"end\":565},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"9fea1c3a-8171-4a64-b63b-3e1024aa180b\",\"uuid\":\"edeb6b4c-3954-481f-b31e-a90423762219\",\"toh\":\"toh12\"}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\". Also, the characteristic of not ceasing and the feelings, conceptions, conditioning factors, and consciousness are something free of duality, and \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":565,\"end\":713}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"free from creating duality\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":713,\"end\":739},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"9fea1c3a-8171-4a64-b63b-3e1024aa180b\",\"uuid\":\"755c8e85-c56a-4128-9d5c-690eb8a3188e\",\"toh\":\"toh12\"}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\". Again, saying ‘feelings, conceptions, conditioning factors, and consciousness’ is to \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":739,\"end\":826}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"quantify\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":826,\"end\":834},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"da120fb0-fc39-419b-9f2e-d54611ad0639\",\"uuid\":\"caa8111b-4e63-4a68-bad1-a8f9f4f2b2ac\",\"toh\":\"toh12\"}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\" something free of duality.\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":834,\"end\":861}}]}]},{\"type\":\"passage\",\"attrs\":{\"uuid\":\"79e8dd53-d750-4d85-9dea-02b17e03c4da\",\"sort\":12446,\"type\":\"translation\",\"label\":\"1.93\",\"alignments\":{\"toh12\":{\"folioUuid\":\"e3e90550-ca9b-49de-a681-4e1aa763fbcf\",\"toh\":\"toh12\",\"tibetan\":\"བཅོམ་ལྡན་འདས་དེ་ལྟར་ཤེས་རབ་ཀྱི་ཕ་རོལ་ཏུ་ཕྱིན་པ་ལ་ཆོས་ཐམས་ཅད་རྣམ་པ་ཐམས་ཅད་དུ་ཉེ་བར་རྟོག་ན། དེའི་ཚེ་གཟུགས་ཉེ་བར་མི་རྟོགས་གཟུགས་ཉེ་བར་མི་འཛིན་གཟུགས་སྐྱེ་བར་ཡང་དག་\\nཔར་རྗེས་སུ་མི་མཐོང་གཟུགས་འགག་པར་ཡང་དག་པར་རྗེས་སུ་མི་མཐོང་། དེ་བཞིན་དུ་ཚོར་བ་མ་ཡིན་འདུ་ཤེས་མ་ཡིན་འདུ་བྱེད་རྣམས་མ་ཡིན། རྣམ་པར་ཤེས་པ་ཉེ་བར་མི་རྟོགས་རྣམ་པར་ཤེས་པ་ཉེ་བར་མི་འཛིན་རྣམ་པར་ཤེས་པ་སྐྱེ་བར་ཡང་དག་པར་རྗེས་སུ་མི་མཐོང་རྣམ་[F.16.a]པར་ཤེས་པ་འགག་པར་ཡང་དག་པར་རྗེས་སུ་མི་མཐོང་ངོ་། །དེ་ཅིའི་སླད་དུ་ཞེ་ན། འདི་ལྟར་གཟུགས་ཀྱི་སྐྱེ་བ་མ་མཆིས་པ་གང་ལགས་པ་དེ་ནི་གཟུགས་མ་ལགས། གཟུགས་ཀྱི་འཇིག་པ་མ་མཆིས་པ་གང་ལགས་པ་དེ་ནི་གཟུགས་མ་ལགས་ཏེ། དེས་ན་\\nསྐྱེ་བ་མ་མཆིས་པ་དང་གཟུགས་ཞེས་བགྱི་བ་འདི་ནི་གཉིས་སུ་མ་མཆིས་ཤིང་གཉིས་སུ་བགྱིར་མ་མཆིས་སོ། །དེས་ན་འཇིག་པ་མ་མཆིས་པ་དང་གཟུགས་ཞེས་བགྱི་བ་འདི་ནི་གཉིས་སུ་མ་མཆིས་ཤིང་གཉིས་སུ་བགྱིར་མ་མཆིས་ཏེ། གང་ཡང་འདི་སྐད་དུ་གཟུགས་ཞེས་བགྱི་བ་\\nའདི་ནི་གཉིས་སུ་མ་མཆིས་པའི་གྲངས་སུ་གཏོགས་སོ། །\",\"folioNumber\":15,\"volumeNumber\":33}}},\"content\":[{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":0,\"end\":976,\"uuid\":\"79e8dd53-d750-4d85-9dea-02b17e03c4da\"},\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"“Therefore, O \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":0,\"end\":14}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Blessed One\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":14,\"end\":25},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"7bf45dd5-3e8d-4495-bc65-ecf0a51d3597\",\"uuid\":\"e63a5643-6fdf-4be2-ab43-0636d4a1f32d\",\"toh\":\"toh12\"}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\", at the time when a bodhisattva is deeply reflecting upon all things as all the aspects in the perfection of wisdom, he or she does not go close to physical forms, arrive at physical forms, identify their arising, or identify their cessation. Likewise, he or she does not go close to feelings, conceptions, conditioning factors, or consciousness, arrive at them, identify their arising, or identify their cessation. Why is that? To explain, physical forms’ nature of not arising is not the same as the so-called physical forms. Physical forms’ nature of not ceasing is not the same as the so-called physical forms. This being said, the characteristic of not arising and the physical forms are something free of duality, and \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":25,\"end\":750}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"free from creating duality\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":750,\"end\":776},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"9fea1c3a-8171-4a64-b63b-3e1024aa180b\",\"uuid\":\"374daa53-ad8b-4332-bc73-8592812ee200\",\"toh\":\"toh12\"}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\". Also, the characteristic of not ceasing and the physical forms are something free of duality, and \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":776,\"end\":876}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"free from creating duality\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":876,\"end\":902},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"9fea1c3a-8171-4a64-b63b-3e1024aa180b\",\"uuid\":\"f4d55f5c-0eeb-4ea3-9cc1-4288e373b793\",\"toh\":\"toh12\"}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\". Again, saying ‘physical forms’ is to \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":902,\"end\":941}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"quantify\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":941,\"end\":949},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"da120fb0-fc39-419b-9f2e-d54611ad0639\",\"uuid\":\"5bd8d4e7-d62f-47b8-8c75-ffa7f3639f39\",\"toh\":\"toh12\"}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\" something free of duality.\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":949,\"end\":976}}]}]},{\"type\":\"passage\",\"attrs\":{\"uuid\":\"78b30325-12fd-43ac-a3b6-428edbe79976\",\"sort\":12458,\"type\":\"translation\",\"label\":\"1.94\",\"alignments\":{\"toh12\":{\"folioUuid\":\"e34b511d-ae13-4ff5-9e4a-484e3e026c39\",\"toh\":\"toh12\",\"tibetan\":\"དེ་བཞིན་དུ་འདི་ལྟར་ཚོར་བའི་གང་ལགས་པ་དང་། འདུ་ཤེས་ཀྱི་གང་ལགས་པ་དང་། འདུ་བྱེད་རྣམས་ཀྱི་གང་ལགས་པ་དང་། འདི་ལྟར་རྣམ་པར་ཤེས་པའི་སྐྱེ་བ་མ་མཆིས་པ་གང་ལགས་པ་དེ་ནི་རྣམ་པར་ཤེས་པ་མ་\\nལགས། རྣམ་པར་ཤེས་པའི་འཇིག་པ་མ་མཆིས་པ་གང་ལགས་པ་དེ་ནི་རྣམ་པར་ཤེས་པ་མ་ལགས་ཏེ། དེས་ན་སྐྱེ་བ་མ་མཆིས་པ་དང་རྣམ་པར་ཤེས་པ་ཞེས་བགྱི་བ་འདི་ཡང་གཉིས་སུ་མ་མཆིས་ཤིང་གཉིས་སུ་བགྱིར་མ་མཆིས་སོ། །དེས་ན་འཇིག་པ་མ་མཆིས་པ་དང་རྣམ་\\nཔར་ཤེས་པ་ཞེས་བགྱི་བ་འདི་ཡང་གཉིས་སུ་མ་མཆིས་ཤིང་གཉིས་སུ་བགྱིར་མ་མཆིས་ཏེ། གང་ཡང་འདི་སྐད་དུ་རྣམ་པར་ཤེས་པ་ཞེས་བགྱི་བ་འདི་ནི་གཉིས་སུ་མ་མཆིས་པའི་གྲངས་སུ་གཏོགས་སོ།། །།ཤེས་རབ་ཀྱི་ཕ་རོལ་ཏུ་ཕྱིན་པ་བརྒྱད་སྟོང་\\nབ། བམ་པོ་གཉིས་པ། \",\"folioNumber\":16,\"volumeNumber\":33}}},\"content\":[{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":0,\"end\":885,\"uuid\":\"78b30325-12fd-43ac-a3b6-428edbe79976\"},\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"“Likewise, the characteristic of not arising of feelings, conceptions, conditioning factors, and consciousness is not the same as the so-called feelings, conceptions, conditioning factors, and consciousness. The characteristic of not ceasing of feelings, conceptions, conditioning factors, and consciousness is not the same as the so-called feelings, conceptions, conditioning factors, and consciousness. This being said, the characteristic of not arising and the feelings, conceptions, conditioning factors, and consciousness are something free of duality, and \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":0,\"end\":562}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"free from creating duality\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":562,\"end\":588},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"9fea1c3a-8171-4a64-b63b-3e1024aa180b\",\"uuid\":\"e9dab906-f8b7-4470-b01c-47d0502a06d2\",\"toh\":\"toh12\"}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\". Also, the characteristic of not ceasing and the feelings, conceptions, conditioning factors, and consciousness are something free of duality, and \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":588,\"end\":736}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"free from creating duality\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":736,\"end\":762},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"9fea1c3a-8171-4a64-b63b-3e1024aa180b\",\"uuid\":\"7ac75ce2-8c3c-4fc6-984a-4349a66e5e42\",\"toh\":\"toh12\"}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\". Again, saying ‘feelings, conceptions, conditioning factors, and consciousness’ is to \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":762,\"end\":849}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"quantify\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":849,\"end\":857},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"da120fb0-fc39-419b-9f2e-d54611ad0639\",\"uuid\":\"157dc4da-ad57-4148-ad78-e6c14df78496\",\"toh\":\"toh12\"}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\" something free of duality.”\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":857,\"end\":885}}]}]},{\"type\":\"passage\",\"attrs\":{\"uuid\":\"dad1e3b3-771f-49f5-b081-71b8124db489\",\"sort\":12466,\"type\":\"translation\",\"label\":\"1.95\",\"alignments\":{\"toh12\":{\"folioUuid\":\"e34b511d-ae13-4ff5-9e4a-484e3e026c39\",\"toh\":\"toh12\",\"tibetan\":\"དེ་ནས་ཚེ་དང་ལྡན་པ་ཤཱ་རིའི་བུས་ཚེ་དང་ལྡན་པ་རབ་འབྱོར་ལ་འདི་སྐད་ཅེས་སྨྲས་སོ། །དེའི་ཕྱིར་ཚེ་དང་ལྡན་པ་རབ་འབྱོར་གྱིས་ཇི་སྐད་སྨྲས་པའི་དོན་བདག་གིས་ཤེས་པ་དེ་ལྟར་ན་བྱང་ཆུབ་སེམས་དཔའ་ཡང་སྐྱེ་བ་མེད་པ་ཡིན་ནོ། །ཚེ་དང་ལྡན་པ་རབ་འབྱོར་\\nགལ་ཏེ་ཡང་བྱང་ཆུབ་སེམས་དཔའ་ཡང་སྐྱེ་བ་མེད་པ་ཡིན་ན་བྱང་ཆུབ་སེམས་དཔའ་དཀའ་བ་སྤྱད་པ་སྤྱོད་པའམ་སེམས་ཅན་རྣམས་ཀྱི་ཕྱིར་སྡུག་བསྔལ་གང་ཡིན་པ་དེ་དག་ཉམས་སུ་མྱོང་བའི་དོན་དུ་སྤྲོ་བ་ཡང་ཅི་ཞིག་ཡོད། \",\"folioNumber\":16,\"volumeNumber\":33}}},\"content\":[{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":0,\"end\":401,\"uuid\":\"dad1e3b3-771f-49f5-b081-71b8124db489\"},\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Then the \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":0,\"end\":9}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"venerable\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":9,\"end\":18},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"91107107-3f31-4442-8365-9099041efadf\",\"uuid\":\"671387bf-f4fe-435c-bcd1-f302e1b05d6e\",\"toh\":\"toh12\"}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\" \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":18,\"end\":19}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Śāriputra\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":19,\"end\":28},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"3df1bcb6-86da-4978-8191-8dbd8f56b919\",\"uuid\":\"60e8893e-de3c-4877-b2e9-e75959e216ad\",\"toh\":\"toh12\"}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\" said this: “To explain the meaning of \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":28,\"end\":67}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Venerable\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":67,\"end\":76},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"91107107-3f31-4442-8365-9099041efadf\",\"uuid\":\"25d3ff3c-91dd-41be-8f12-b4d0c346ea85\",\"toh\":\"toh12\"}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\" \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":76,\"end\":77}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Subhūti\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":77,\"end\":84},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"22f9f523-3d5f-4683-ac40-82bee1ab5a5f\",\"uuid\":\"ef8e4406-15e7-4dcf-b8fa-5a65a10703f1\",\"toh\":\"toh12\"}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"’s teaching as I understand it, even bodhisattvas are free of arising. That said, \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":84,\"end\":166}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Subhūti\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":166,\"end\":173},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"22f9f523-3d5f-4683-ac40-82bee1ab5a5f\",\"uuid\":\"7113178d-ac55-4134-9740-a8b8cffe4218\",\"toh\":\"toh12\"}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\", if even bodhisattvas are free of arising, then how can they \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":173,\"end\":235}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"go about life\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":235,\"end\":248},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"e47cf8c1-4e22-4e6c-af2f-a5dac51c76a0\",\"uuid\":\"2b852a8a-61a6-4313-aa0f-8669bd88223e\",\"toh\":\"toh12\"}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\" performing difficult noble deeds? How are they able to subject themselves to those \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":248,\"end\":332}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"sufferings\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":332,\"end\":342},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"999cad0b-8e8c-42d8-aac9-011a2dec26ca\",\"uuid\":\"36dc356a-7f15-4b12-8333-38e285f8483e\",\"toh\":\"toh12\"}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\", to which they subject themselves for the sake of beings?”\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":342,\"end\":401},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"endNoteLink\",\"attrs\":{\"notes\":[{\"endNote\":\"8b058934-48b6-4dd9-b60b-e799f6c937da\",\"label\":\"190\",\"uuid\":\"fae857c3-7a5b-497a-a558-5bed7bddfd26\",\"start\":401,\"end\":401,\"location\":\"end\",\"toh\":null}]}}]}]}]},{\"type\":\"passage\",\"attrs\":{\"uuid\":\"95725458-2e8e-4b9c-af3c-67003568796b\",\"sort\":12483,\"type\":\"translation\",\"label\":\"1.96\",\"alignments\":{\"toh12\":{\"folioUuid\":\"e34b511d-ae13-4ff5-9e4a-484e3e026c39\",\"toh\":\"toh12\",\"tibetan\":\"$60\",\"folioNumber\":16,\"volumeNumber\":33}}},\"content\":[{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":0,\"end\":1487,\"uuid\":\"95725458-2e8e-4b9c-af3c-67003568796b\"},\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"At this, the \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":0,\"end\":13}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"venerable\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":13,\"end\":22},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"91107107-3f31-4442-8365-9099041efadf\",\"uuid\":\"65f4915e-b23d-49be-bf7a-9de61c4f213b\",\"toh\":\"toh12\"}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\" \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":22,\"end\":23}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Subhūti\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":23,\"end\":30},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"22f9f523-3d5f-4683-ac40-82bee1ab5a5f\",\"uuid\":\"f7e2383e-7fc7-4856-850b-f801932f8567\",\"toh\":\"toh12\"}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\" said to the \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":30,\"end\":43}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"venerable\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":43,\"end\":52},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"91107107-3f31-4442-8365-9099041efadf\",\"uuid\":\"33afe401-5d76-4142-96fa-3ffbd9c519c0\",\"toh\":\"toh12\"}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\" \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":52,\"end\":53}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Śāriputra\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":53,\"end\":62},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"3df1bcb6-86da-4978-8191-8dbd8f56b919\",\"uuid\":\"655a4232-b6e6-4069-bcbc-08cf99c3c555\",\"toh\":\"toh12\"}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\", “I do not hold that a bodhisattva \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":62,\"end\":98}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"great being\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":98,\"end\":109},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"be37efde-2f63-40d0-8e8e-e93b3b3a581e\",\"uuid\":\"38f6267f-18a9-45db-a54a-beb5a682d319\",\"toh\":\"toh12\"}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\" is \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":109,\"end\":113}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"going about life\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":113,\"end\":129},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"e47cf8c1-4e22-4e6c-af2f-a5dac51c76a0\",\"uuid\":\"fb932962-687a-4c0f-980f-22edf212f844\",\"toh\":\"toh12\"}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\" performing difficult noble deeds, or that a bodhisattva \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":129,\"end\":186}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"great being\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":186,\"end\":197},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"be37efde-2f63-40d0-8e8e-e93b3b3a581e\",\"uuid\":\"d37d4b6f-2854-4891-8520-5b1dff706e35\",\"toh\":\"toh12\"}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\" is someone who \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":197,\"end\":213}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"goes about life\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":213,\"end\":228},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"e47cf8c1-4e22-4e6c-af2f-a5dac51c76a0\",\"uuid\":\"6a3288e3-23e3-4685-bf62-f268fbc03efe\",\"toh\":\"toh12\"}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\" with a conception of any noble deeds as difficult. Why not? To explain, it is not possible to bring about the benefit of immeasurable and \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":228,\"end\":367}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"innumerable\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":367,\"end\":378},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"9283281d-0ed6-4831-9df9-d4d8da920713\",\"uuid\":\"11d58c55-fc81-492b-9552-18d0739590dd\",\"toh\":\"toh12\"}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\" beings after developing the conception of noble deeds as difficult. Rather, it is only after developing the conception of them as easy. That is to say, it is only after developing the conception of all beings‍—male or female‍—as mothers, fathers, daughters, or sons that a bodhisattva \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":378,\"end\":664}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"great being\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":664,\"end\":675},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"be37efde-2f63-40d0-8e8e-e93b3b3a581e\",\"uuid\":\"22607684-6513-4898-9870-615011b46543\",\"toh\":\"toh12\"}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\" \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":675,\"end\":676}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"goes about life\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":676,\"end\":691},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"e47cf8c1-4e22-4e6c-af2f-a5dac51c76a0\",\"uuid\":\"3dee6cfb-cb25-46a9-a70b-f8e05ff80acd\",\"toh\":\"toh12\"}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\" performing the noble deeds of a bodhisattva. Based on that, a bodhisattva \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":691,\"end\":766}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"great being\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":766,\"end\":777},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"be37efde-2f63-40d0-8e8e-e93b3b3a581e\",\"uuid\":\"aa732e78-8503-4647-a127-517329b1f55c\",\"toh\":\"toh12\"}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\" should develop the conception of all beings as mothers, fathers, sons, and daughters until finally he or she develops the conception of them as his or her very own self, thinking, ‘Just as I must liberate myself from all \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":777,\"end\":999}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"sufferings\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":999,\"end\":1009},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"999cad0b-8e8c-42d8-aac9-011a2dec26ca\",\"uuid\":\"083b1ca4-4b66-4a33-aa5f-6eab36125517\",\"toh\":\"toh12\"}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\" by absolutely every means and in absolutely every way, just so I must liberate all sentient beings from all \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":1009,\"end\":1118}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"sufferings\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":1118,\"end\":1128},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"999cad0b-8e8c-42d8-aac9-011a2dec26ca\",\"uuid\":\"a1380ae8-d143-45d6-b212-ceaf312b9fef\",\"toh\":\"toh12\"}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\" by absolutely every means and in absolutely every way. Likewise, I must develop this conception with respect to all sentient beings and I shall not desert any of them. I must liberate all these beings from immeasurable amounts of \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":1128,\"end\":1359}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"sufferings\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":1359,\"end\":1369},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"999cad0b-8e8c-42d8-aac9-011a2dec26ca\",\"uuid\":\"71f21713-522a-4be3-be2e-365c88c526f0\",\"toh\":\"toh12\"}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\" and I must not develop a \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":1369,\"end\":1395}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"mindset\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":1395,\"end\":1402},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"ad0b5c96-5b65-496d-bb1c-0e4fa6ad3bf4\",\"uuid\":\"1b081db1-cf5b-4264-bae4-449b78d3dfd3\",\"toh\":\"toh12\"}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\" that is hostile toward them, even if I am being cut to pieces a hundred times over!’\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":1402,\"end\":1487}}]}]},{\"type\":\"passage\",\"attrs\":{\"uuid\":\"d56009d3-d8d4-471c-ba64-e33b48d1cbdd\",\"sort\":12519,\"type\":\"translation\",\"label\":\"1.97\",\"alignments\":{\"toh12\":{\"folioUuid\":\"3b808f47-21b7-422d-aaef-3b36dc970e4f\",\"toh\":\"toh12\",\"tibetan\":\"གལ་ཏེ་སེམས་\\nཅན་དེ་ལྟར་གནས་ན་དཀའ་བ་བྱེད་པའི་འདུ་ཤེས་སུ་སྤྱོད་པ་མ་ཡིན་ནོ། །དཀའ་བ་བྱེད་པའི་འདུ་ཤེས་སུ་གནས་པ་མ་ཡིན་ནོ། །\",\"folioNumber\":16,\"volumeNumber\":33}}},\"content\":[{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":0,\"end\":228,\"uuid\":\"d56009d3-d8d4-471c-ba64-e33b48d1cbdd\"},\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"“In precisely this way, a bodhisattva \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":0,\"end\":38}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"great being\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":38,\"end\":49},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"be37efde-2f63-40d0-8e8e-e93b3b3a581e\",\"uuid\":\"b2abc56a-b4c9-4da4-bac7-2f602c0a4976\",\"toh\":\"toh12\"}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\" should \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":49,\"end\":57}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"develop the proper mindset\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":57,\"end\":83},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"ea400c56-f5af-4899-8997-425cbffa9950\",\"uuid\":\"1665f9aa-52aa-4e77-9b2c-872b3356bb0c\",\"toh\":\"toh12\"}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\". Furthermore, if he or she comes to abide with a \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":83,\"end\":133}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"mindset\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":133,\"end\":140},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"ad0b5c96-5b65-496d-bb1c-0e4fa6ad3bf4\",\"uuid\":\"90388590-cf7a-4358-aed4-c8383b8d1532\",\"toh\":\"toh12\"}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\" like this, then he or she will not abide with a conception of noble deeds as difficult.\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":140,\"end\":228}}]}]}]}]\n"])</script><div hidden id="S:5"><div dir="ltr" data-orientation="horizontal" data-slot="tabs" class="flex flex-col w-full gap-